      <li><a href="/docs/guide/quickstart">Quickstart</a></li>
      <li><a href="/docs/api/model">API</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/javirm3/TFM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a></li>
